{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I knew what was happening, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went through the gas chambers, and before they were cremated, you know, they were-- their teeth were pulled out, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, so everybody was profiting from this place, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is-- there were thousands of Nazis that were-- this is the way they were making a lot of money, you know-- gold and whatever was found there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was working here till January of 1945.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, we were clean, you know, and these SSs, they needed some pills for anything, the doctors always gave it to them, you see.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had certain amount of pills.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you what, what we had, because-- you know, this I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What could which?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, for anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For food, or for-- food, cigarettes, or what-- you know, anything of that sort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was there till January of-- January the 20th, 1945.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, on the 20th, that night-- prior to the 20th, several thousands of people were driven out of Auschwitz by the SS.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were taken away on transports somewhere else, and we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were burning the cards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, they had thousands and thousands, hundreds of thousands of cards, because the Germans were chronic-- you know, they were very accurate.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They recorded everybody that was tattooed, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had them on a card to take-- you know, on a card system-- you know, where you came from-- so mine, with many others that were given-- tattooed numbers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were destroying all these hundreds of thousands of cards in January.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was-- they had a big pile of it dumped in Auschwitz, and they were pouring gasoline on it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were burning this.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
